2026-02-13
Features
- Added soft Rebind integration (`com.rebind`) for Open/Close hotkeys; Configurable Miners now registers keybind rows under `MODS > Configurable Miners` when Rebind is installed.
- Added automatic Rebind registration retry during runtime to handle load-order timing.
- Added Rebind handle cleanup on plugin unload.
- Config panel now shows local Open/Close key capture rows only when Rebind is not installed.
Bug Fixes
- Fixed an IMGUI layout/repaint mismatch that could throw `ArgumentException: Getting control ...` when opening or interacting with the Configurable Miners UI.

2026-02-11
Features
- Routed local persistence JSON object/array splitting helpers through shared `RBN.Modlib.Persistence.JsonSettingsUtils` (`ReadNestedRaw` and `SplitTopLevelObjects`) so both mods use one parser path.
- Switched Config panel layout to shared `RBN.Modlib.UI.UiConfigMenuShell.DrawScrollablePaddedContent(...)` to reuse common padded+scrollable panel behavior.

Bug Fixes
- Reduced parser drift risk between mods by removing duplicate nested/object parsing logic in Configurable Miners.

2026-02-10
Features
- Moved UI style creation to `RBN.Modlib.UiStylePresets` and removed local style-builder duplication.
- Added `stylePreset` setting (currently `style_1`) with config-file options metadata for forward-compatible style packs.
- Added in-game `UI Style` config row to cycle available shared style presets.
- Updated style initialization to auto-refresh when style preset or window opacity changes at runtime.
- Added support for shared `style_2` preset via the same `UI Style` selector.
- Switched settings JSON helper primitives to shared `RBN.Modlib.Persistence.JsonSettingsUtils`.
- Switched toast system to shared `RBN.Modlib.UI.UiToastQueue` and shared `ToastType`.
- Switched RGB border + solid-rect drawing to shared `RBN.Modlib.UI.UiDrawUtils`.
- Switched centered slider primitive to shared `RBN.Modlib.UI.UiConfigRowUtils`.
- Replaced Open/Close key rebinding with true keybind capture using shared `RBN.Modlib.UI.UiKeybindCaptureState` (press key / Escape clears / reset button).
- Switched hover prompt card rendering to shared `RBN.Modlib.UI.UiHoverPromptRenderer`.
- Switched config panel container layout to shared `RBN.Modlib.UI.UiConfigMenuShell` single-panel shell.
- Switched config float/int/toggle row behavior to shared `RBN.Modlib.UI.UiConfigRowWidgets` (through local wrappers).

Bug Fixes
- Fixed first-open style rendering issue where `style_1` background could appear missing until changing styles; style cache is now refreshed when opening UI.
- Fixed Config panel Open/Close key rebinding flow so it no longer cycles preset keys and now captures actual user key presses.
- Removed remaining local JSON pass-through helpers and switched settings/miners/presets parsing and writing directly to `RBN.Modlib.Persistence.JsonSettingsUtils`.

2026-02-09
Features
- Migrated shared utility logic to `RBN.Modlib` and wired Configurable Miners to consume it.
- Added project/solution reference to `RBN.Modlib` for shared foundation usage.
- Reused shared UI/player-control helpers for cursor unlock, player control toggle, and UI manager suppression.
- Reused shared reflection/save-path helpers for game singleton lookup and active save folder path handling.

Features
- Added configurable group quantity (whole-number slider + textbox), with dynamic group names/picker/toggle support and backward-compatible settings persistence.

- Separated Ore Clusters from Geodes in output filtering: Ore Clusters are always selectable and no longer gated by Geode toggles.
- Improved output picker readability by brightening Coal, Copper, and Ruby text colors against dark button backgrounds.
- Further improved picker readability by brightening Coal more and adding brighter Amethyst/Celestite text (including geode entries).
- Refactored base plugin file into partials: lifecycle loop/UI draw, UI state/cursor control, and debug clear-event hooks are now split out for easier maintenance.
- Split runtime into focused partials (Selection, Spawn, OutputOptions, Groups) and kept Runtime core for shared/apply/utility flow.
- Split persistence into focused partials: Settings, Miners data, Presets, and JsonHelpers for cleaner maintenance.
- Split UI into focused partials: Windows, Rows, Panels, Controls, and Visuals to reduce single-file complexity.
- Removed empty ConfigurableMiners.UI.cs shell after UI partial split cleanup.
- Updated presets layout to explicit two columns (1/3/5/7 left, 2/4/6/8 right) with center spacing.
Bug Fixes
- Fixed Revert so miner spawn rate/probability restore from original definition instead of keeping edited runtime values.
- Fixed miner selection false positives by ignoring trigger colliders and requiring in-view cone targeting.
- Fixed M-key miner selection to fall back to hover-distance targeting so prompt and open behavior stay consistent.
- Reduced TrySpawnOre patch overhead by skipping interception unless override-configured miners exist; added 5s grace before pruning missing saved miner entries.
